.vercel

# ── God-generated one-off debug artifacts ────────────────────────────────
# The god agent occasionally writes query results / schema dumps / debug
# scripts when diagnosing itself. These are useful ephemeral debugging
# context but shouldn't pollute the public repo.

# Root-level SHOUTY_CASE doc files (only uppercase + underscores allowed
# are LICENSE and README.md which are above, so anything else is junk)
/[A-Z][A-Z0-9_]*.md
!/README.md
!/LICENSE
!/INSTALL.md
!/CONTRIBUTING.md

# One-off query / export / validation scripts (kept the pattern matching
# god's naming conventions — its real utilities live under agent names)
scripts/query-*.ts
scripts/query-*.mjs
scripts/query-*.sql
scripts/execute-*.ts
scripts/execute-*.mjs
scripts/execute-bounded-*.ts
scripts/export-*.ts
scripts/export-*.mjs
scripts/export-*.sql
scripts/export-*.json
scripts/export_*.sql
scripts/export_*.json
scripts/validate-*.ts
scripts/validate-*.mjs
scripts/validate-*.sql
scripts/validate_*.sql
scripts/test-*.ts
scripts/test-*.mjs
scripts/inspect-*.ts
scripts/fetch-*.ts
scripts/extract-*.ts
scripts/schema-*.ts
scripts/supabase-ddl*.sql

# Ephemeral schema/query docs under docs/ (keep agent-patterns.md, INSTALL.md, etc.)
docs/AGENT_EXEC*.md
docs/DISMISS_*.md
docs/SCHEMA_*.md
docs/TODOS_*.md
docs/*_schema.md
docs/*-query-examples.sql
docs/agent_exec_*
